{"tid":664570,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"【夏天冷氣論】根本用風扇就係戇鳩","createTime":"2018-05-14T07:37:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-14T08:35:47.000Z","uid":104096,"like":1,"dislike":21,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"9fdc95c106c8710f8fbdaf43248ca8127ff6950c","tid":664570,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:37:08.000Z","msg":"風扇先發電已經排好撚多二氧化碳<br />\n仲要風扇你吹果吓就覺得涼<br />\n屌實際啲粒子郁快咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係令整體溫度上升<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n咪又係熱戇鳩鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌即係燒煤燒天然氣已經熱<br />\n用風扇仲熱戇鳩鳩<br />\n所以計我話冷氣就最撚實際<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n你燒完啲煤又可以排番啲冷氣出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n等價交換<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔會好似風扇咁戇鳩<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"07968897e8c392dff041ebf4e9d0d49f7e519dea","tid":664570,"uid":51880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:39:34.000Z","msg":"其實好似三份熱氣換一份冷氣"},{"pid":"bdd5066e798330ea23854519630dd921d95946cf","tid":664570,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"07968897e8c392dff041ebf4e9d0d49f7e519dea","tid":664570,"uid":51880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:39:34.000Z","msg":"其實好似三份熱氣換一份冷氣"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:40:24.000Z","msg":"有冇專家出嚟解釋吓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973a82b96d1eb341844cccee0f49c2dd3b507081","tid":664570,"uid":104096,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T07:42:35.000Z","msg":"咁都有負皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cada68dee516b1fd53b8a3536419cbeac184094f","tid":664570,"uid":33875,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score